===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[Ophioglossum]]'' (a genus) + [[-phyta]]

===Proper noun===
'''Ophioglossophyta'''

#{{botany}}: A [[botanical name]] for a [[taxon]] within [[kingdom]] [[Plantae]] that includes the [[adder's tongue]]s, [[moonwort]]s, and [[grape-fern]]s. The taxon is traditionally given the [[rank]] of a [[division]].

